snippet: An S.U.V. found burning in the desert with five bodies inside was registered to the home of a missing family of five, including three children, the police in Tempe said Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: An S.U.V. found burning in the desert with five bodies inside was registered to the home of a missing family of five, including three children, the police in Tempe said Tuesday.

headline.main: Arizona: 5 Dead in Desert May Be Missing Family
